Title: Journey to Jaguar Mountain
Plot: Baby Jaguar is full of pride when he thinks that he is big enough to get to the top of Jaguar Mountain.  Diego and Baby Jaguar's mother agree to meet him at the top of Jaguar Mountain.  Does Baby Jaguar have the skills to make it up to the top, or will the obstacles prove to be too much trouble for him to handle?
Writer: Chris Gifford, Ligiah Villalobos, Valerie Walsh
